gw.processes

Class WorkQueueInstrumentation

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.processes.WorkQueueInstrumentation

  • public class WorkQueueInstrumentation
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains custom instrumentation fields of a work queue. Note that WorkQueueInstrumentation is saved along with the InstrumentedWorkerTask, and each task starts with an empty instrumentation. All getters and setters throw an IllegalArgumentException if the specified field is unknown or has different type. User: akorostov Date: 1/18/13
